					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Nintendo claimed in a Gameboy Color brochure aimed at developers that the MBC5 controller was backwards compatible with all prior MBCs except for the MBC3's Real Time Clock functionality.  Aside from the Rumble and RTC capabilities, I can understand that in the case of the MBC3.  But what about the MCB1 and MCB2?</div>

